dct_title_s: Map showing location of Panama Canal : as recommended by the Isthmian Canal Commission of 1899-1902
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours and hachures. Depths shown by soundings.; Supplement to National Geographic, October 1905.; Oriented with north toward upper left.; In lower left margin: Andrew B. Graham Co., lithographers, Washington, D.C.; In lower right margin: Oliver B. Harden del.; Includes notes and profile of canal.
